column2: SELECT   m.id as [id], str(m.ra,#,#) AS ra, str(m.dec,#,#) AS dec,   str(sp.modelMag_u,#,#) as u,str(sp.modelMagErr_u,#,#) as err_u,      str(sp.modelMag_g,#,#) as g,str(sp.modelMagErr_g,#,#) as err_g,     str(sp.modelMag_i,#,#) as r,str(sp.modelMagErr_i,#,#) as err_i,        str(sp.modelMag_r,#,#) as r,str(sp.modelMagErr_r,#,#) as err_r,     sp.plate, sp.fiberid, sp.mjd, sp.z, sp.zwarning into mydb.listMgIIphot_t2 from MyDB.listMgIIphot AS m             OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON n.objID=sp.objID     LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.specobjID=sp.specobjID     LEFT OUTER JOIN emissionLinesPort as g ON g.specobjID = sp.specobjID     JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objID =sp.objID         WHERE (sp.z >= #) OR (pz.z >= #) AND (sp.class = &&&)    ORDER by m.id
